{"tid":2300011,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"富商邱達昌妻子確診 澄清不屬跳舞群組","createTime":"2020-11-25T07:31:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T09:11:48.000Z","uid":21470,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"fea522983625b1cc2c59af2b8b5916d592f9fa99","tid":2300011,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T07:31:10.000Z","msg":"邱達昌妻子吳惠平確診 否認屬跳舞群組<br />\n<br />\n有線寬頻主席邱達昌的妻子邱吳惠平確診感染新型冠狀病毒。邱吳惠平發表聲明，指得知上星期四的一個飯局中，有朋友確診，為防止病毒進一步擴散及盡公民責任，她立刻進行自願病毒檢測，獲告知確診。邱吳惠平強調自己從不跳舞，並非跳舞群組一員，又指自己現時身體情況良好，正在醫院接受治療，感謝所有為抗疫努力的醫護人員。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2367882\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2367882&d=Z5fxCpLMP6GgpQ63MmTuwkBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=b9eafa24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2367882</a>"},{"pid":"1e2c8803d4f0ebfb3c762c58b834546923b52526","tid":2300011,"uid":273157,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T07:32:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁姐係建興群組啦"},{"pid":"c59a906d55c5fef874599e2cdeef8dec59b8400a","tid":2300011,"uid":2772,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T07:32:57.000Z","msg":"好心D師奶跟呢隻真淫西學下野<br />\n叫鴨就叫鴨<br />\n洗乜用跳舞做藉口"},{"pid":"94428997db82aea8a9c27d4ea8caf0bc71a83813","tid":2300011,"uid":56063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T07:33:02.000Z","msg":"同跳舞割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5b394bf74d6b70138440d57a7dad73166861ffe","tid":2300011,"uid":158613,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T07:33:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d5c1d5857f94f91e7a390626feb8618615a97e7","tid":2300011,"uid":103156,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T07:34:27.000Z","msg":"從不跳舞，直接開波就做"},{"pid":"a56d3d18ff566dd5c12